async with get_temp_empty_database() as temp_empty_database:
    await temp_empty_database.insert(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV, 1, symbol=
        'xyz', price='1', date='01')
    await temp_empty_database.create_index(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV, [
        'symbol', 'timestamp'])
    assert await temp_empty_database.select(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV) == [(
        1, 'xyz', '1', '01')]
